result.name: TYFUN DIMSUM

reviews.text: This restaurant provides decent dim sum with reasonable price but offers few dim sum options to be dim sum restaurant.

The food was tasty, dim sum were good. Can have a good chat with friends there. Especially like the spicy dumplings and the deep fried shrimp dumplings. The purple sweet potato steam buns were nice too, runny fillings and not too sweet. Could be a place if u to try if u like Cantonese dim sum.
Dum sums are served hot, delicious and looks pretty cute. Definitely will be liked by children and adults

Dim sum here is great, and most of them with attractive outlook.  Taste not great, but at least not disappointing you.
If you come here at night, it's comfortable as most of their customers are for lunch only.  And the restaurant is beautiful, well decorated.
My favorite dish here will be their fried rice
Dim sum was good but expect to wait a long time for the food to arrive. Severely understaffed.

reviews.text: Still a good venue to shop luxurious goods and enjoy tea
Some good deals

When I first visited the Eiffel tower in 2001 I was stunned by the amount of tourists from all over the world. It was beautiful knowing that they all came to one spot on The same day to enjoy in the simple magnificence of Paris. Little did I know that all those years ago I would again visit the Eiffel tower in 2015 with a whole different set of unique people.

Amazing shopping experience you have here! After shopping, I feel tired and have foot and body treatment in Happy Valley. There is nice place to visit -- Zenxes Foot Retreat. Here you can meet so many foreign residents enjoying Zenxes service like me too. Super!
Nice, high end stores.  I was there for the baby and kids section.   Nice selection of quality stuff.
